install in modules directory

usage:
Latest Album:
http://scottnath.com/gallery3/index.php/externals?block_id=latest_album

Latest Photo:
http://scottnath.com/gallery3/index.php/externals?block_id=latest_photo

Random Album:
http://scottnath.com/gallery3/index.php/externals?block_id=random_album

Random Photo:
http://scottnath.com/gallery3/index.php/externals?block_id=random_photo

then, if you wanted to call this on an outside page you would do this:

<?php
$imglink = file_get_contents("http://scottnath.com/gallery3/index.php/randimg?block_id=latest_album", "r");
echo "$imglink";
?>